    "defaultMessage": "Add and remove sequences",
    "description": "Alt imatge 2 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step1.alt": {
    "defaultMessage": "Sequence 1 with pictograms and button to add a new sequence",
    "description": "Alt imatge pas 1 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step1.description": {
    "defaultMessage": "On the edit page, search for words in the search box (separated by commas) and pictograms will appear automatically in the active sequence. Click the + button to create a new sequence.",
    "description": "Descripció pas 1 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step2.alt": {
    "defaultMessage": "Two sequence tabs visible, sequence 2 active",
    "description": "Alt imatge pas 2 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step2.description": {
    "defaultMessage": "Click any tab to switch to a different active sequence. Each sequence has its own independent content. Search for new words to fill sequence 2.",
    "description": "Descripció pas 2 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step3.alt": {
    "defaultMessage": "View of both sequences with size increased globally",
    "description": "Alt imatge pas 3 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step3.description": {
    "defaultMessage": "In the View page, the \"Apply to all\" toggle lets you adjust the size and spacing of all sequences at once. Move the size control to see the change applied globally.",
    "description": "Descripció pas 3 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step4.alt": {
    "defaultMessage": "View with sequence 2 individually adjusted to a different size",
    "description": "Alt imatge pas 4 múltiples seqüències"
  },
  "news.multiple-sequences.step4.description": {
    "defaultMessage": "Disable \"Apply to all\" to configure each sequence independently. Expand the accordion for the sequence you want to adjust and change its size or spacing without affecting the others.",
    "description": "Descripció pas 4 múltiples seqüències"
  },
